    <text type="note" xml:lang="ru" xml:id="letter-09111"> 
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <date when-custom="1789-06-30">1789 г. 30 июня.</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p> На <name type="event" ref="events.xml#ochak01">взятие <placeName ref="places.xml#och01">Очакова</placeName></name>: <hi rend="italic">Усердием и храбростию</hi>. На <name type="event" ref="events.xml#crime02">занятие <placeName ref="places.xml#cri01">Крыма</placeName></name>: <hi rend="italic">Кротостию смирен противник</hi>. На население и устроение <placeName ref="places.xml#eka01">Екатеринославской губернии</placeName>: <hi rend="italic">Степи населил, устроил</hi>.
                <note type="editorial">
                    In this note Catherine writes about the projects of three personal portrait medals in the honor of <persName ref="people.xml#pot01">G.A. Potemkin</persName> for his merits. The medals were sent to Potemkin on <date when-custom="1789-09-07">September 7 1789</date> (
                    <bibl>
                        <title ref="works.xml#medali01">K istorii sozdaniia trekh medalei v chest' G.A. Potemkina</title>
                        , <biblScope unit="pp">pp. 68.</biblScope>
                    </bibl>
                    ).
                </note>
            </p>
        </body>
